description:
This comprehensive course covers every aspect of med-school admissions. If you want to learn how to stand out in a crowded applicant pool and land your top spot in medical school, this is the course for you.

The materials start from the very beginning, providing a deep dive into who you are, why you want to become a physician, and how to keep your self-esteem intact.

The course continues with the technical aspects of producing a "winning" application. It covers succeeding in your courses and the MCAT, writing personal statements, interviewing secrets, and more.

Download the free workbook that accompanies the course. Personalize it, make it your own, and use it as your roadmap to success.
title: Your Kick-Ass Guide to Getting into Medical School
